06:14.080 --> 06:14.920
Pagi, Tante.

06:14.960 --> 06:15.680
Pagi, Kakek. Pagi, Yuanbao.

06:15.680 --> 06:16.840
Yuanbao, ayo sini duduk.

06:16.840 --> 06:17.520
